characterDescription:
Warren is a master Skybreaker who trains the squires beneath him outside the Skybreaker fortress near the Purelake.
He tells the trainees that theirs is a test of martial competence. That they must train to fight, if the Desolation truly has begun.

characterDetails.Appearance: Szeth thinks that he looks strange in the garb of a Marabethian lawkeeper, chest bare and shoulders draped with the short, patterned cloak. The Azish are normally so proper, overly encumbered with robes and hats.
